headline: ASML Stock Rises As Semiconductor Equipment Group Rallies
summary: ASML stock hit its highest price in just over a year on Tuesday as investor sentiment improves for the semiconductor equipment segment.

headline: 2 Nasdaq 100 Stocks with Impressive Fundamentals and 1 Facing Headwinds
summary: While the Nasdaq 100 (^NDX) is filled with cutting-edge technology and consumer companies, not all are on solid footing. Some are dealing with declining demand, high costs, or regulatory pressures that could limit future upside.
